	(132,'_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51','<div class=\"rss-widget\"><ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.org/news/2014/07/wordpress-4-0-beta-2/\'>WordPress 4.0 Beta 2</a> <span class=\"rss-date\">July 18, 2014</span><div class=\"rssSummary\">WordPress 4.0 Beta 2 is now available for download and testing. This is software still in development, so we don’t recommend that you run it on a production site. To get the beta, try the WordPress Beta Tester plugin (you’ll want “bleeding edge nightlies”). Or you can download the beta here (zip). For more of what’s new in version 4.0, check out […]</div></li></ul></div><div class=\"rss-widget\"><ul><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wptavern.com/wpbeginner-reaches-funding-goal-to-build-two-new-schools?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wpbeginner-reaches-funding-goal-to-build-two-new-schools\' title=\'Earlier this month, WPBeginner hosted a huge giveaway to celebrate its 5th birthday. Alongside the giveaway, Syed Balkhi wanted to build two schools this year in Guatemala through the Pencils of Promise charity. To do so, he needed $50,000. He ended up with $50,584. Once the schools are built, Balkhi will travel to Guatemala to take photos and videos. WPBegi\'>WPTavern: WPBeginner Reaches Funding Goal To Build Two New Schools</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wptavern.com/brian-richards-leaves-webdevstudios-to-work-on-wpsessions-full-time?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=brian-richards-leaves-webdevstudios-to-work-on-wpsessions-full-time\' title=\'After nearly two years at WebDevStudios acting as a development lead, Brian Richards is stepping down to spend more time on his side project, WPSessions. Richards is the lead developer of the Startbox theme framework and is one of the organizers of WordCamp Grand Rapids set to take place August 15-17, 2014. WPSessions was launched in 2013 and provides high q\'>WPTavern: Brian Richards Leaves WebDevStudios To Work On WPSessions Full-Time</a></li><li><a class=\'rsswidget\' href=\'http://wordpress.tv/2014/07/24/walter-ebert-die-htaccess-richtig-nutzen/\' title=\'\'>WordPress.tv: Walter Ebert: Die .htaccess richtig nutzen</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"rss-widget\"><ul><li class=\'dashboard-news-plugin\'><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=\'http://wordpress.org/plugins/ml-slider/\' class=\'dashboard-news-plugin-link\'>Meta Slider</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=ml-slider&amp;_wpnonce=eea7f36a46&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'Meta Slider\'>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>','no'),
